description:
This ti is a commission of @Zorglub

Abigail Spencer is an American actress. Spencer has built a successful career in both television and film, known for her versatile performances and ability to portray a wide range of characters.

Spencer gained recognition for her role as Amantha Holden in the critically acclaimed television series "Rectify." In addition to "Rectify," Spencer has appeared in numerous other television shows, including "Suits," "Grey's Anatomy," "Timeless," and "True Detective." She also had a recurring role in the hit series "Mad Men" as Suzanne Farrell.
